## Korean landing-page strings for Contract Studio.
##
## v0.5/design-landing — DESIGN.md §3 rewrite (2026-05-17).
##
## The landing template's msgids ARE the Korean copy themselves —
## they're written natively in home.html.heex. Because Gettext falls
## back to the msgid when the msgstr is empty, leaving these msgstrs
## empty here would still produce the intended Korean rendering. We
## keep redundant Korean msgstrs (== msgid) so a future
## `mix gettext.extract --merge` run doesn't accidentally delete them
## and so machine-translation tools that ignore empty msgstrs still
## pick them up.
##
## #. TODO native-speaker review — copy reviewed against the
## mature-visual-language memory ("legal tooling, not startup-pop"):
##   - "구체화합니다" (give concrete form to) — chosen over generic
##     "변환" / "만듭니다" for editorial gravitas.
##   - "남습니다" (is preserved / remains) — passive, ledger-like.
##   - "비공개 베타. 초청제로 운영합니다." — retained from prior copy.
msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Language: ko\n"
"Plural-Forms: nplurals=1; plural=0;\n"

